# Unit cube mesh fixture for test_worlds_maniskill's mesh_path spawn
# path. Hand-crafted so tests don't depend on any downloaded dataset.
# 8 vertices (+/-0.5 on each axis), 12 triangles (2 per face, 6 faces).
v -0.5 -0.5 -0.5
v  0.5 -0.5 -0.5
v  0.5  0.5 -0.5
v -0.5  0.5 -0.5
v -0.5 -0.5  0.5
v  0.5 -0.5  0.5
v  0.5  0.5  0.5
v -0.5  0.5  0.5
f 1 2 3
f 1 3 4
f 5 7 6
f 5 8 7
f 1 5 6
f 1 6 2
f 2 6 7
f 2 7 3
f 3 7 8
f 3 8 4
f 4 8 5
f 4 5 1
